                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Powell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-05-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 27, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Powell reports the establishment of a Provisional Government, with Canal as
                    President, Nord as secretary of war, St. Fort Colin as secretary of the
                    interior, Jérémie as secretary for foreign relations, Cesarions as secretary of
                    agriculture, Dennery as secretary of finance, and Lalanne as secretary of
                    justice, and that affairs are rather better.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
